    <item>
      <title>Aeriva: A Mini Autonomous Quadrotor Platform</title>
      <link>https://yichengchen.com/project/aeriva/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://yichengchen.com/project/aeriva/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Aeriva&lt;/strong&gt; - This name is a combination of &amp;ldquo;aero&amp;rdquo; (meaning air) and &amp;ldquo;diva&amp;rdquo; (suggesting a stylish and confident personality).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In March 2023, I began to design, assemble, and test this drone from scratch. So far, four drones of this type have been made and used in various scientific research and competitions in my lab.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agile and safe&lt;/strong&gt;: Aeriva is built upon a 3.5-inch cinewhoop frame with Kakute H7 mini flight controller, making it exceptionally agile, compact and safe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High computing performance&lt;/strong&gt;: Aeriva is equipped with NVIDIA Jetson Orin NX, facilitating it with strong onboard computing capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;specifications&#34;&gt;Specifications&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Component&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Specs&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Computer&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;NVIDIA Jetson Orin NX&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Camera&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Intel RealSense D435&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Stack&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Kakute H7 mini + Tekko32 F4 4in1 mini 45A ESC&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Dimension&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;152mm motor-to-motor&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Motors&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;RCinpower GTS V3 2104-T-1800kv&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Propellers&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Gemfan D90S&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Battery&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;6S 1200mah 150C&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;accomplishments-based-on-aeriva&#34;&gt;Accomplishments based on Aeriva&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Scientific research:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../../publication/neo-planner/&#34;&gt;Learning to Initialize Trajectory Optimization for Vision-Based Autonomous Flight in Unknown Environments&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
