    <item>
      <title>2018 Beihang Robot Competition</title>
      <link>https://yichengchen.com/project/beihang-robot-competition/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Dec 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://yichengchen.com/project/beihang-robot-competition/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;challenge&#34;&gt;Challenge&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This competition requires participants to build a robot with the following functions: line tracking, obstacle avoidance, object grabbing, and Bluetooth remote control. Participants will be ranked based on the quality and duration of completing a series of tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solutions&#34;&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Built a multifunctional wheeled robot from scratch: Used Arduino as the computer. Incorporated infrared modules and ultrasonic modules for line tracking and obstacle avoidance in a reactive manner. Made a cylinder with a rubber band that can take objects in. Achieved remote control via the Bluetooth module and an Android Application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /project/beihang-robot-competition/images/robot_v2_hu90c2a3e3e7753b33eed288fb95860fdd_8610684_ba28686758e7ecc3a8b6d4c9a55994c9.webp 400w,
               /project/beihang-robot-competition/images/robot_v2_hu90c2a3e3e7753b33eed288fb95860fdd_8610684_5b435e5db3695e3414a3e53c2a70a237.webp 760w,
               /project/beihang-robot-competition/images/robot_v2_hu90c2a3e3e7753b33eed288fb95860fdd_8610684_1200x1200_fit_q100_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;https://yichengchen.com/project/beihang-robot-competition/images/robot_v2_hu90c2a3e3e7753b33eed288fb95860fdd_8610684_ba28686758e7ecc3a8b6d4c9a55994c9.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;570&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

▲ The final version of our robot&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;Highlight&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We ranked the 4th place in the final.&lt;/p&gt;
